{%- comment -%}
  LC design-token emission — Phase 4 A5/A6 + MISSING-MOBILE-HEADER-BG wiring.

  Rendered inside layout/theme.liquid <head>. Emits LC-owned CSS custom
  properties that interpolate from admin settings at compile time. Pattern
  mirrors Flex's theme.css.liquid (compile-time Liquid interpolation, not
  var() chains at runtime), so admin changes propagate when settings_data
  updates trigger a theme.css recompile.

  Previously these tokens were static hex literals in assets/custom.css :root.
  Moving them here makes admin control real for the first time.
{%- endcomment -%}
{% style %}
  :root {
    /* Header — mobile */
    --color-header-bg: {{ settings.mobile_header_background | default: '#4d4d4d' }};

    /* Footer — desktop + mobile */
    --color-footer-bg: {{ settings.footer_background | default: '#4d4d4d' }};
  }
{% endstyle %}
